Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 25th Feb, 2026
App Name: Closet Cycle
Location: United States

Closet Cycle (“we,” “our,” or “us”) values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our mobile application and related services (the “App”).

By using Closet Cycle, you agree to this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect

We collect the following categories of information:

A. Personal Information

When you create an account, we collect:

Email address

First name and last name

Phone number (optional)

This information is used to create and manage your account.

B. Account & Authentication Data

We use Firebase Authentication to manage user accounts. This includes:

Login credentials (securely stored by Firebase)

Email verification status

Password reset records

We do not store your password in plain text.

C. Profile Information

You may choose to provide:

Username

Bio

Profile picture

Location (city/state)

Wardrobe preferences

This information is visible to other users.

D. Location Information

We collect:

GPS location or manually entered location

Location is used to:

Display your general location on your profile

Improve trade relevance and item recommendations

We do NOT perform background tracking or real-time monitoring.

E. User-Generated Content

We collect and store:

Photos and videos uploaded for listings

Item descriptions

Tags and metadata

Messages between users

Ratings and reviews

This content is necessary to operate the platform.

F. Payment Information

Payments are processed securely through Stripe (and/or PayPal, if enabled).

We do NOT store:

Credit card numbers

Full payment details

Stripe processes payment data according to its own privacy policy.

G. Shipping Information

When a trade is accepted, users provide:

Shipping name

Shipping address

Shipping labels are generated through Shippo. Addresses are only shared after trade acceptance.

H. Device Information

We may automatically collect:

Device type

Operating system

App version

Basic analytics data

This helps us improve performance and fix bugs.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:

Create and manage user accounts

Enable trading and payments

Generate shipping labels

Facilitate messaging

Provide customer support

Send notifications (trade updates, messages, etc.)

Improve app functionality and recommendations

Prevent fraud and abuse

Comply with legal obligations

We do NOT sell your personal data.

3. How We Share Information

We may share information in the following situations:

With Other Users

Profile information

Listings

Ratings and reviews

Location (general area only)

Shipping address (only after trade acceptance)

With Service Providers

We share limited information with:

Firebase (Google Cloud) – authentication, storage, database

Stripe – payment processing

Shippo – shipping label generation

Push notification services

These providers are contractually required to safeguard your information.

Legal Requirements

We may disclose information if required by law, court order, or government request.

4. Data Security

We use industry-standard security measures, including:

HTTPS encryption

Firebase security rules

Secure cloud storage

Role-based access controls

However, no system is 100% secure. Use of the App is at your own risk.

